<TR valign="top">
    <TD width="1%" nowrap align="left">*</TD>
    <TD width="3%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="96%">The Stepdown Date is the earlier of the distribution date following the
reduction of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero, or September&nbsp;17, 2007. At the Stepdown
Date, principal payments made on the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes may begin to be
paid pro-rata with the Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the prospectus for complete
information concerning the Stepdown Date.</TD>
</TR>

    <TD width="96%">The Stepdown Date is the earlier of the distribution date following the
reduction of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero, or March&nbsp;17, 2008. At the
Stepdown Date, principal payments made on the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes
may begin to be paid pro-rata with the Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the
prospectus for complete information concerning the Stepdown Date.</TD>

<P><HR noshade><P>
<H5 align="left" style="page-break-before:always">&nbsp;</H5><P>

<P align="left" style="width: 100%; padding: 2px; font-size: 10pt; background: #000000; color: #FFFFFF"><B>X. 2003-A Accrued Interest Factors</B>


<DIV align="center">
<TABLE style="font-size: 10pt" cellspacing="0" border="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">

<!-- Begin Table Head --><TR valign="bottom">
    <TD width="7%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="48%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="4%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="20%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="4%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
</TR>
<TR style="font-size: 8pt" valign="bottom">
    <TD>&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD>&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD>&nbsp;</TD>

<TR valign="top">
    <TD width="1%" nowrap align="left">*</TD>
    <TD width="3%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="96%">The Stepdown Date is the earlier of the distribution date following the
reduction of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero, or June&nbsp;15, 2008. At the
Stepdown Date, principal payments made on the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes may
begin to be paid pro-rata with the Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the prospectus
for complete information concerning the Stepdown Date.</TD>

<H5 align="left" style="page-break-before:always">&nbsp;</H5><P>
<DIV style="font-family: 'Times New Roman',Times,serif">


<P align="left" style="font-size: 10pt"><B>SLM Private Credit Student Loan Trust 2003-C</B><BR>
<B>Quarterly Servicing Report</B><BR>
<B>Report Date: 11/30/2004 Reporting Period: 9/1/04-11/30/04</B>



<P align="left" style="width: 100%; padding: 2px; font-size: 10pt; background: #000000; color: #FFFFFF"><B>I. Deal Parameters</B>


<DIV align="center">
<TABLE style="font-size: 8pt" cellspacing="0" border="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<!-- Begin Table Head -->
<TR valign="bottom">
    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="3%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="48%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>

    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="6%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="2%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD width="5%">&nbsp;</TD>
</TR>
<TR style="font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; background: #000000" valign="bottom">
    <TD>&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD>&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD nowrap align="left" colspan="3"><B>Student Loan Portfolio Characteristics</B></TD>

    <TD width="2%" nowrap align="right">*</TD>
    <TD width="1%">&nbsp;</TD>
    <TD>The Stepdown Date is the earlier of the distribution date
following the reduction of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero and
September&nbsp;15, 2008. At the Stepdown Date, principal payments
made on the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes may begin to be paid
pro-rata with the Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the prospectus for
complete information concerning the Stepdown Date.</TD>

of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero and March&nbsp;16, 2009. At the Stepdown Date, principal
payments made on the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes may begin to be paid pro-rata with the
Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the prospectus for complete information concerning the
Stepdown Date.</TD>

<P align="left" style="width: 100%; padding: 2px; font-size: 10pt; background: #000000; color: #FFFFFF"><B>III.

<P align="left" style="font-size: 10pt"><b>* Percentages may not total 100% due to rounding</b>

<P align="center" style="font-size: 10pt">6
</DIV>

    <TD width="96%">The Stepdown Date is the earlier of the distribution
date following the reduction of the Class&nbsp;A Notes to zero and
June&nbsp;15, 2009. At the Stepdown Date, principal payments made on
the Class&nbsp;B and Class&nbsp;C Notes may begin to be paid pro-rata
with the Class&nbsp;A Notes. See the prospectus for complete
information concerning the Stepdown Date.</TD>
